    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "What we need to do is change the `_update` override in ERC1155Supply so that the supply update is done after `super._update`.\r\n\r\nHowever, this introduces a reentrancy issue, so at the same time we have to refactor `ERC1155._update` so that it does not do the acceptance check at the end.\r\n\r\nI would propose to have two functions: `_update` and `_updateChecked` where the second one calls `_update` and the transfer acceptance check. All of the token functionality would be impemented in terms of `_updateChecked`, but the override have to be done on `_update`.",
